Revision history for markdown

0.04 2026-04-30
    - replaced the remaining external document converters with a Perl-only module stack
    - removed `aptfile` and `brewfile` in favor of `cpanfile`
    - switched markdown-to-pdf rendering to `PDF::API2`

0.03 2026-04-30
    - made positional file arguments the primary CLI flow for `markdown.convert`
    - added visible stderr progress logging for long-running conversion steps

0.02 2026-04-30
    - replaced the macOS pdf package contract with `weasyprint`
    - added runtime fallback from `wkhtmltopdf` to `weasyprint` for markdown to pdf conversion

0.01 2026-04-30
    - created the initial `markdown` skill with CLI conversion support for markdown, html, and pdf
    - added Docker-verified tests for route selection, output naming, and fake-tool conversion flows
